---
const quickLinks = [
  { label: 'Where to Live', href: '/where-to-live' },
  { label: 'House Prices', href: '/house-prices' },
  { label: 'Schools', href: '/schools' },
  { label: 'Commuting', href: '/commuting' },
  { label: 'Is It Worth It?', href: '/lifestyle' },
  { label: 'Investment', href: '/investment', highlight: true },
];
---

<section
  aria-labelledby="hero-heading"
  class="section-pad"
  style="background-color: #F9F7F4;"
>
  <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px;">

    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <div style="width: 28px; height: 2px; background-color: #3D5A3E; flex-shrink: 0;" />
      <span
        style="font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: #3D5A3E;"
      >
        Independent Relocation Intelligence &mdash; Cheshire, England
      </span>
    </div>

    <h1
      id="hero-heading"
      style="font-family: Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(32px, 5.5vw, 52px); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.12; color: #1C1C1E; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 28px; max-width: 720px;"
    >
      Moving to Cheshire?
      <br />
      <span style="color: #3D5A3E;">Here's everything you need to know.</span>
    </h1>

    <p
      style="font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 19px); line-height: 1.7; color: #444444; max-width: 660px; margin-bottom: 36px;"
    >
      An independent guide to buying a home in Cheshire - covering house prices, schools,
      commute times, area comparisons, and the honest case for and against relocating to Cheshire.
      Whether you're a London relocator weighing up the cost of living or a Manchester
      professional checking commute options, this is the data you need. Updated quarterly
      from primary sources.
    </p>

    <div
      style="border-left: 3px solid #3D5A3E; background-color: rgba(61, 90, 62, 0.04); padding: 16px 20px; margin-bottom: 44px;"
    >
      <p
        style="font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #1C1C1E; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 4px;"
      >
        No estate agent spin. No sponsored content. Just answers.
      </p>
      <p
        style="font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #777777; margin: 0;"
      >
        All data sourced from ONS, Ofsted, National Rail, and official council records.
        Last updated: February 2026.
      </p>
    </div>

    <nav aria-label="Page sections" style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px;">
      {quickLinks.map((link) => {
        const isHighlight = 'highlight' in link && link.highlight;
        return (
          <a
            href={link.href}
            class={isHighlight ? 'hero-link hero-link--highlight' : 'hero-link'}
            style={`font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: ${isHighlight ? '#C4933F' : '#3D5A3E'}; border: 1px solid ${isHighlight ? 'rgba(196,147,63,0.5)' : '#3D5A3E'}; padding: 9px 18px; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.01em; transition: background-color 0.15s ease, color 0.15s ease; display: inline-block;`}
          >
            {link.label}
          </a>
        );
      })}
    </nav>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-link:hover {
    background-color: #3D5A3E !important;
    color: #FFFFFF !important;
  }
  .hero-link--highlight:hover {
    background-color: #C4933F !important;
    color: #FFFFFF !important;
  }
</style>
